{"tid":1583886,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[教學po] 勇武和理非請入！","createTime":"2019-09-21T00:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T08:40:43.000Z","uid":322592,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9fc6e94d7b2ee605b00038665bb0b29912770867","tid":1583886,"uid":322592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:32:49.000Z","msg":"嗱 小弟第一次開po 如有錯漏不足之處 敬請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n古乳有暈: 跑得快好世界<br />\n今時今日香港隨時都有俾狗追嘅可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以呢個po係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">教跑步</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1.</span> 如果你見到狗要極速閃人 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好腳踭落地</span> 腳踭落地包你跑得慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.</span> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好望後面</span> 望咗一定會收慢腳步<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3.</span> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">俾力擺手</span> 物理嘅反作用力 向後chok得愈勁 個身就推得愈前<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n好啦如果有巴絲打直情想跑快啲跑長啲 我教你！你要嘅係中長跑嘅能力 速度耐力兼備<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲畜龍其實都跑得幾撚快 好多本身都係跑得之人 好多都係啲乜撚特別部隊啲人 平時乜都唔使做就係操fit體能同練跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">不過唔使怕！每星期肯練兩三日跑就ok! 夠哂對付上十幾KG裝嘅狗 夠哂止暴制亂<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(私了)</span>之後甩身</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n訓練詳情如下:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">星期一/二: 8x200m 休兩分鐘 出8-9成力<br />\n星期三/四: 3k 出6-7成力 唔好一開始鳩衝 留力吖<br />\n星期五/六: 5x150m 休三分鐘 出盡力</span><br />\n記住慢跑熱身同拉筋！練習與練習之間最好休息一日！<br />\n香港好撚多運動場㗎！只係用你一個禮拜兩三日時間！同我練跑吖！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(覺得小弟講得好廢又想跑快啲嘅巴絲打可以自行上youtube學 記住揾中長跑教學/how to run 800m)</span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n齊上齊落 缺一不可"},{"pid":"9fbaa7f714bb771cba78a7a023697982b5eb3ad7","tid":1583886,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:33:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"4d38563e7f6492cfa8cd0ef97d2d58912cfbc2c9","tid":1583886,"uid":322592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T06:27:46.000Z","msg":"冇人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0277273fbc35cea9b48bda7dd76ae3becf9cb40","tid":1583886,"uid":226617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d38563e7f6492cfa8cd0ef97d2d58912cfbc2c9","tid":1583886,"uid":322592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T06:27:46.000Z","msg":"冇人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:30:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"07e04103565015b5668c927b3ddec204427d1445","tid":1583886,"uid":53034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:40:43.000Z","msg":"pushhhh"}]}